WEBVTT

00:03:28.812 --> 00:03:32.064
in a given community
or with respect to some issue --

00:03:32.088 --> 00:03:33.978
the economy, education.

00:03:35.538 --> 00:03:39.464
I've done my share
of that kind of journalism

00:03:39.488 --> 00:03:40.873
over many years.

00:03:42.524 --> 00:03:45.145
But then George Zimmerman
killed Trayvon Martin,

00:03:46.621 --> 00:03:51.233
followed by this unending string
of high-profile police shootings

00:03:51.257 --> 00:03:52.976
of unarmed Black people,

00:03:53.000 --> 00:03:55.521
the rise of the Black
Lives Matter movement,

00:03:55.545 --> 00:03:58.608
Dylann Roof and the Charleston massacre,

00:03:58.632 --> 00:04:00.286
#OscarsSoWhite --